claim.claim-text:
1. A polymeric composite product, comprising: 
a polymer matrix; 
a tannin containing cellulosic material; 
calcium carbonate; and 
an amount of a compound, having at least two functional groups capable of reacting with tannins present in said tannin containing cellulosic material, sufficient to prevent leaching and deposition of said tannins on a surface of the product when contacted with water.

12. A polymer composite product, comprising: 
from 35 to 75 wt % of PVC; 
from 25 to 65 wt % of oak flour; 
a non-zero amount of calcium carbonate up to about 15 wt % based on PVC content; and 
from 0.1-5% of succinic anhydride.
